ady for you to step inside. Until then, know that you've taken the first step toward something deeper than notifications and feedsâ€”you've said yes to the beginnings of brotherhood.\n                    </p>\n                  </td>\n                </tr>\n              </table>\n\n              <!-- Divider -->\n              <table role=\"presentation\" width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"margin:30px 0;\">\n                <tr>\n                  <td style=\"height:1px;background:#1a1a1a;\" class=\"divider\">&nbsp;</td>\n                </tr>\n              </table>\n\n              <!-- Footer -->\n              <table role=\"presentation\" width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"0\">\n                <tr>\n                  <td align=\"center\" style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:22px;color:#666666;\" class=\"text-secondary\">\n                    <p style=\"margin:0 0 12px 0;font-style:italic;\">\n                      \"From strangers to brothers, forged through prayer.\"\n                    </p>\n                    <p style=\"margin:0 0 8px 0;\">\n                      <a href=\"https://forge-app.io/manifesto\" style=\"color:#ff4500;text-decoration:none;font-weight:600;\">Read our manifesto</a>\n                    </p>\n                    <p style=\"margin:0 0 8px 0;\">\n                      Questions? <a href=\"{{supportUrl}}\" style=\"color:#ff4500;text-decoration:none;font-weight:600;\">Contact us</a>\n                    </p>\n                    <p style=\"margin:0;font-size:12px;color:#555555;\">\n                      Â© {{year}} Forge. All rights reserved.\n                    </p>\n                  </td>\n                </tr>\n              </table>\n\n            </td>\n          </tr>\n        </table>\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  </table>\n</body>\n</html>",
